data.description: Charming Large spacious 3 bedroom 3 bath 2 story home with finished walkout basement to a fenced in yard. Great location in Alton, just minutes to restaurants, shopping, Etc. Lots of updates including room addition with new master bedroom/master bath with walk in closet and on the lower level family room addition, also you will see a nice size deck out the master bedroom to relax , and a deck off the kitchen of the main level great for grilling and entertaining, call your agent and schedule your showing today.
